Git

****************************************************

Git installation 

On ubuntu 
$sudo apt-get update
$sudo apt-get install -y git

git --version

On RHEL/CentOS/Fedora
$sudo yum -y update
$sudo yum install -y git

* Git commands

1. To configure name and email globally for all users on a specific machine
git config --global user.name BR1947
git config --global user.email balakrishna.r1947@gmail.com


2. create git repository directory
mkdir <gitreponame>

3. Initialize git repository
cd git_repo/
git init

